---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for CloudyUnicorn Tools. Understand the terms, guidelines, and disclaimers for using our suite of online calculators."
>
  <div class="relative min-h-[calc(100vh-16rem)] bg-background py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Grid Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern bg-grid-fade pointer-events-none opacity-20"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12 animate-fade-in">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-600 dark:hover:text-neutral-300">Tools</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Terms of Service</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-mono">
          Last Updated: June 16, 2026 &bull; Effective Immediately
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Block -->
      <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-8 leading-relaxed">

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and utilizing the web-based applications, calculator tools, and metadata provided on <strong>CloudyUnicorn Tools</strong> ("the Site"), you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not consent to these terms, you should immediately cease all use of our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">2. Description of Services</h2>
          <p>
            CloudyUnicorn Tools provides clean, high-precision, client-side online calculators (including but not limited to the Age Calculator, BMI Calculator, and Calories Calculator). These utilities are designed for general informational and educational utility only. 
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">3. Medical & Professional Disclaimer</h2>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-red pl-4 py-1 text-neutral-555 italic">
            <strong>Important notice:</strong> The calculations, estimations, and guidance outputs provided by our BMI and Calories calculators are based on standardized mathematical algorithms (such as the Harris-Benedict formula, Mifflin-St Jeor equation, WHO scale, etc.). They do not constitute medical advice, clinical diagnoses, or professional nutritional programs. Always consult a qualified physician or healthcare provider before initiating diet, exercise, or health-related adjustments.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">4. Permitted Use</h2>
          <p>
            You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use the Site for personal, non-commercial purposes. You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 text-neutral-500">
            <li>Engage in automated scraping, data mining, or harvesting of Site structures or codebases.</li>
            <li>Use the Site in any manner that could damage, disable, overburden, or degrade our hosting infrastructure.</li>
            <li>Incorporate the Site's calculators into third-party applications without explicit attribution.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All custom code, styling sheets, visual assets, layouts, and site structures are the intellectual property of CloudyUnicorn. You may copy the mathematical formulations for custom use, but reproducing the exact visual representations or layouts is prohibited.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">6. Disclaimer of Warranties & Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            THE SITE AND ALL CALCULATORS ARE PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. CLOUDYUNICORN DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO accuracy, completeness, or reliability of calculations. UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES SHALL CLOUDYUNICORN BE LIABLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF THE USE OR INABILITY TO USE THE TOOLS.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">7. Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Your continued use of the Site following modifications constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions regarding these Terms of Service, please reach out to us at <!--email_off--><a href="mailto:support@cloudyunicorn.com" class="text-neutral-905 dark:text-white hover:underline font-medium">support@cloudyunicorn.com</a><!--/email_off-->.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }
</style>
